Our first Creator Retreat for our team at The Creator Collective powered by @nfm_lending is a WRAP. An experience I’ll never forget. Beyond grateful for our team of pioneers! As a group we average roughly 10M+ organic views every week and have roughly 4M followers in total. If you told me years ago that this would translate to thousands of potential home buyers wanting to work with our team and an entire division built around leveraging social media, I would’ve had my doubts. It’s been an absolute roller coaster ride and I am so grateful to be on the ride with these amazing people. Excited to watch our team continue to grow and educate consumers at scale.
